{"tid":2156312,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點撚解要支持蘋果日報啲廣告？","createTime":"2020-08-14T10:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T16:02:42.000Z","uid":194588,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8ce05919f103cb65b5ab2d2174caff2c2b9ea6be","tid":2156312,"uid":194588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:57:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><p class=\"center\"><span class=\"xx-large\">點解要支持果啲廣告？</span></p></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><ins><span class=\"x-large\">1. 武肺已經令到經濟好差</span></ins></span><br />\n你要知道喺蘋果落廣告要幾貴<br />\n要哂A1全頁落廣告已經要20萬<br />\n其他頁數落廣告都要成幾萬銀㗎<br />\n而且落廣告唔代表間商店生意好㗎<br />\n而家加埋武肺更加唔使多講啦<br />\n已經有幾間黃店告急啦<br />\n就好似今日嘅潮食閣咁<br />\n如果商戶落咗廣告冇人知冇人買<br />\n真係會蝕到仆街㗎<br />\n我哋一齊同黃店捱過武肺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><ins><span class=\"x-large\">2. 廣告係蘋果其中一個主要收入</span></ins></span><br />\n上述都講到其實落廣告係幾貴㗎啦<br />\n如果啲黃店落咗廣告冇人支持<br />\n仲會唔會有人落廣告啊！<br />\n好似今日29個廣告咁<br />\n已經可以令蘋果賺到80-90萬㗎啦<br />\n大家一齊撐住僅有嘅良心媒體好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><ins><span class=\"x-large\">3. 拉攏商戶加入/擴大黃圈</span></ins></span><br />\n其實支持廣告嘅時候係同時抗爭緊<br />\n因為啲廣告對黃色經濟圈真係好重要！<br />\n而家有好多網店/冷門小店係黃嘅都冇人知！<br />\n加上呢場係持久戰！<br />\n支持落咗廣告嘅商戶絕對能擴大我方陣營！<br />\n香港人係時候將自己嘅消費完全黃色化啦！<br />\n睇啱有邊啲廣告用得著就真係收藏低好冇？<br />\n我要以後一蚊都唔俾藍店/中資！<br />\n講真呢啲野都做唔到點樣持續抗爭？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"violet\"><ins><p class=\"center\">我而家俾個Daily Task香港人：</p></ins></span></span>1. 每日買蘋果日報<br />\n2. 自動波CLS哂啲廣告(comment,like,share佢哋fb/ig page)就算冇人俾Link你都要自覺做！<br />\n3. 多啲去消費落咗廣告嘅商戶！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">我唔撚係同你講緊笑！</span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">唔肯付出幾分鐘CLS<br />\n又唔肯多啲支持黃店嘅<br />\n我抗你老母個臭閪爭咩</span></span>"},{"pid":"525e28f2f0f6a8eb0ca110f4b744aa60b9a6b063","tid":2156312,"uid":194588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:58:19.000Z","msg":"是日蘋果日報廣告：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(感謝隔離po整合)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泰Cool<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E6%B3%B0Cool-101086341417064/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E6%25B3%25B0Cool-101086341417064%2F&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=44b7d023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E6%B3%B0Cool-101086341417064/</a><br />\n<br />\n烘焙&bull;愛麗斯 Alice Loves To Bake<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E7%83%98%E7%84%99%E6%84%9B%E9%BA%97%E6%96%AF-Alice-Loves-To-Bake-111832633848378/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E7%2583%2598%25E7%2584%2599%25E6%2584%259B%25E9%25BA%2597%25E6%2596%25AF-Alice-Loves-To-Bake-111832633848378%2F&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=5b4a0a26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E7%83%98%E7%84%99%E6%84%9B%E9%BA%97%E6%96%AF-Alice-Loves-To-Bake-111832633848378/</a><br />\n<br />\n九份茶舍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jiufenteahouse\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2